OL,3,CMurder investigation after man dies
OL,4,Cfollowing break-in
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after a man died following a
OL,8,Fbreak-in at an apartment building in
OL,9,Feast Belfast, police said.
OL,11,FThe PSNI said emergency services were
OL,12,Fcalled to reports of an assault in the
OL,13,FHolywood Road area in the early hours
OL,14,Fof Tuesday.
OL,16,FThe victim, named by police as 51-year-
OL,17,Fold Nicholas Gordon, was taken to
OL,18,Fhospital, where he later died.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
