OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779117069
OL,3,CMurder investigation after man dies
OL,4,Cfollowing break-in
OL,6,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "We received
OL,7,Fa report at around 8.25am on Tuesday,
OL,8,F12th May of an assault in the Holywood
OL,9,FRoad area, where a number of intruders
OL,10,Fhad entered an apartment building and
OL,11,Fattacked another male, before making
OL,12,Foff.
OL,14,F"We believe the assault took place at
OL,15,Faround 4.45am that morning."
OL,17,FA 24-year-old man and a 49-year-old
OL,18,Fwoman were arrested on suspicion of
OL,19,Faggravated burglary with intent to
OL,20,Fcommit grievous bodily harm.
OL,26,@nD@[OUvD@AOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
