CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779117069
OL,3,CMurder investigation after man dies
OL,4,Cfollowing break-in
OL,6,FBoth have since been released on bail
OL,7,Fpending further enquiries, police
OL,8,Fconfirmed.
OL,10,FThe police statement added: "Sadly,
OL,11,Fthe injured man, 51-year-old Nicholas
OL,12,F(Nicky) Gordon, has now passed away
OL,13,Fand a murder investigation has been
OL,14,Flaunched.
OL,16,F"Our thoughts are with his family at
OL,17,Fthis incredibly difficult time."
OL,26,@rD@]OUxD@AOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
