CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779117069
OL,3,CMurder investigation after man dies
OL,4,Cfollowing break-in
OL,6,F"We would also like to hear from
OL,7,Fanyone who was in the Holywood Road
OL,8,Farea on Tuesday, 12th May between 4am
OL,9,Fand 8.30am and noticed suspicious
OL,10,Fbehaviour to get in touch.
OL,12,F"Residents in this area will continue
OL,13,Fto see a police presence over the next
OL,14,Ffew days, as our investigation
OL,15,Fdevelops."
